HEADWORD: Acarina
<hw>Ac`a*ri"na</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>prop. n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL., from Gr. <?/ a mite.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The order
